<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">警辅人员</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">在 <span>南堤</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">市</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">场巡逻时</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">接到群众求助称</span></p>
